Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the beginning, there was darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所见超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们数个世纪里激起了人们的好奇\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They've intrigued man for centuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样迷惑着天文学家和占星家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}captivating astronomers and astrologers alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在吉萨大金字塔和猎户星座之间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A mysterious alignment...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神秘地排成一条直线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}between the great pyramids of Giza and the stars of Orion...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是一种巧合\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}could have been more than a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是黄道十二宫星座\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And instead of12 zodiac constellations...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是有十三宫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we actually have 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第13个是什么？为何会被忘却呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What is our13th sign, and why was it forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些图形曾经引领船员 穿越危险的水域\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The patterns that once navigated mariners...across treacherous waters...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又引领天文学家去解开"星座"里隐藏的秘密\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}now guide astronomers to uncover the mysteries...that lie within "The Constellations."
