Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.69,0:31:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白超巨星很罕见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}White supergiants are rare...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.61,0:31:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为恒星从红超巨星转变为蓝超巨星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because the star is transitioning...from a red to a blue supergiant...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.53,0:32:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其阶段只能维持几百万年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a phase that only lasts a few million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.96,0:32:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按人类的标准 听起来好像很长的时间了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This may sound like a long time by human standards...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.38,0:32:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 对于恒星来说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but for a star...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.54,0:32:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是其生命周期的1%还不到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's less than one percent of its lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.47,0:32:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于一个以优雅的鸟的名字命名的星座\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For a constellation named after a graceful bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.55,0:32:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天鹅座饱受暴戾岁月的创伤\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cygnus bears the scars of a violent past.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.39,0:32:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天鹅座也是叫做天鹅座环的东西的家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So Cygnus is also home...to something called the Cygnus Loop...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.94,0:32:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一颗超新星的残骸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is a supernova remnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.23,0:32:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上有颗星将自己炸的粉身碎骨\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There was a star that blew itselfto bits, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.44,0:32:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开血盆大口的黑洞 叫做天鹅座X1\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A gaping black hole, called Cygnus X1...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.57,0:32:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就坐落在天鹅的心脏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lies in the swan's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.28,0:32:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天鹅座X1是个8.7太阳质量的黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cygnus X1 is an 8.7 solar mass black hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.53,0:32:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 是太阳质量的8.7倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so that's 8.7 times the mass of our Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.41,0:32:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围绕着另一颗恒星运转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that's orbiting another star.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.67,0:32:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天鹅座X1是第一个记录在案的黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cygnus X1 was the first black hole to ever be recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.67,0:32:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 我们首次发现天鹅座X1\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln fact, we first detected Cygnus X1...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.92,0:32:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非因为是黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}not so much because of the black hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.59,0:32:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它漆黑一团 难以被发觉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because it's black... it's very hard to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.97,0:32:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是因为它对其同伴的影响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but because of its effect on its companion...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.01,0:33:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是颗巨星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is this giant star.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.93,0:33:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 那个黑洞正在慢慢吞噬着同伴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And in fact, the black hole...is slowly devouring the companion...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.85,0:33:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终它可能会把同伴整个吞没\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and eventually it will probably swallow it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.23,0:33:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时星座将会失去一颗星星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And when it does...a constellation will lose a star...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.11,0:33:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们对夜空的看法将会永远改变\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and our perception of the night sky...will change forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.03,0:33:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的夜空持续不断地改变\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our night sky is in constant change.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.66,0:33:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个星座里 星星诞生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Within each constellation, stars are born...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.00,0:33:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 别的星星被黑洞吞噬\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}while others are swallowed by black holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.63,0:33:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一颗超新星的爆发 恒星 星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every supernova explosion, exotic star, and nebula...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.88,0:33:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有一个共同点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has one thing in common...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.43,0:33:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都可以凭借其所在的星座给甄别出来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they are identified...by the constellation they're located in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.68,0:33:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 在我们发明观察它们的高倍望远镜之前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But even before we invented...high-powered telescopes to see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.94,0:33:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座还承担着一个重要的用途\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}constellations served an important purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.90,0:33:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给人们带来不敢掉以轻心的晚间新闻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they brought people...the nightly news that they dared not ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.61,0:34:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是生死攸关的问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt was a question of life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.07,0:34:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧 夜空就是历法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You see, the night sky is a calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.16,0:34:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我们人类最早的科学发明\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That was the very first scientific invention...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.83,0:34:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上的历法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of us humans, the calendar in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.83,0:34:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日出日落 月相变化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The rising and setting of the Sun...the changing phases of the Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.84,0:34:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,群星随季节重现消失\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the seasonal reappearances...and disappearances of the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.68,0:34:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们看到的其实是井井有序\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}people see that there is, in fact...an order to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.85,0:34:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们其实是看到了天上的次序\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They, in fact, see order in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.68,0:34:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对人们预测地球上的事情是有用的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that is useful for them...to anticipate what's happening on the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.02,0:34:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是生存的工具\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's a tool for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.57,0:34:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你仰望天空时看到群星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When you look at the sky...you see these groups of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.19,0:34:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联系着重大事件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that are connected to important events...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.70,0:34:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会提示你以某种方式行动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that would prompt you to behave in certain ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.20,0:34:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或以某种方式进展\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or to move in certain ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.58,0:34:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或耕种 或收获\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or to plant or harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.54,0:34:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了观察星相的季节性变化外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Besides seeing the pattern of stars...changing with the seasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.25,0:34:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古人还进行了另外一项重要的观察\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the ancients made another crucial observation...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.38,0:35:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是影响他们世界的斗转星移\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the shif ting stellar canopy shaped their world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.26,0:35:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路往南的旅行者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Travelers who went a long way south...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.22,0:35:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如 从希腊出发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for example, from Greece...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.06,0:35:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到各种星座\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}started being able to see different constellations...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.77,0:35:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据任何一个在家乡看到过的星座启程\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from any of the constellations...that had been visible in their hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.65,0:35:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 是在告诉你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it's telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.86,0:35:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实是在一个曲面上移动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that you're really moving on a curved surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.69,0:35:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不断改变着你的视野\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and changing your perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.40,0:35:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今 我们了解了地球的形状\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Today we understand the shape of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.57,0:35:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及季节的更替\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the parade of the seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.91,0:35:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 星座并未超出它们的用途\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But constellations haven't outlived their usefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.25,0:35:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在告诉我们地球的情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lnstead of telling us about the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.37,0:35:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是 帮助我们搞明白星星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they're helping us make sense of the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.92,0:35:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座非常像美术馆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A constellation is a lot like an art museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.26,0:35:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在美术馆里 你可以看到艺术家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln an art museum, you will see artists...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.17,0:35:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用的各种材料\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}who have used different kinds of materials...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.51,0:35:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作品 相片 平平常常的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}paintings, photographs, and ordinary objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.60,0:35:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座也有类似的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A constellation also has similar objects...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.64,0:35:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却是不同的材料\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but made of different materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.56,0:35:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中有些有较多的氢或氦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some of them have more helium or hydrogen...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.73,0:35:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者碳 硅 铁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or carbon, silicon, iron...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.61,0:35:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至我们还可以将它们收集起来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and yet we can group them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.82,0:36:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是美术馆 还是星座里收集的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln both cases...the objects that are gathered in an art museum...or a constellation...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.78,0:36:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们都是我们出于某种原因人为收集起来的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they're artificial collections...that we've put together for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.70,0:36:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座像国家那样将天空划分成版图\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like countries, constellations divide the sky into territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.96,0:36:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你说起 猎户座 我就能准确知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When you say "Orion," l know exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.79,0:36:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是哪一部分天空了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what part of the sky you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.79,0:36:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 对于天文学家来说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So to an astronomer...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.96,0:36:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座真的是张方便的地图\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a constellation really is kind of a handy map.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.13,0:36:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是整理东西的方式\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's just a way of organizing things...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.92,0:36:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们就会知道东西所在的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so we kind of know where stuff is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.47,0:36:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使 夜空无边无际\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And even though the night sky is infinite...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.97,0:36:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们只能够看到没有被尘埃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we can see only a sampling of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.81,0:36:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和距离遮挡的很少的星星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before dust and distance blocks our view.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.64,0:36:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你或许会在伸手不见五指的夜晚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You will probably see on a very dark night...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.48,0:36:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭肉眼看到1500到2000颗星星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}maybe 1,500 to 2,000 stars with your naked eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.48,0:36:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 你没有借助望远镜等东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if you're not using binoculars or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.20,0:36:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我们看到的只是外面世界的极小一部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So what we're seeing is only a tiny, tiny fraction...of what's really out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.20,0:36:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就有点像\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That would be sort of like looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.16,0:36:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在美国整个人口 3.5亿人中只看到5个人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at the whole population of the United States...350 million Americans...and seeing five people.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.34,0:37:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人马座 即半人马座 有101颗可见星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Centaurus, or the centaur, contains 101 visible stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.67,0:37:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中两颗 人马座α β\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Two of its stars, Alpha and Beta Centauri...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.51,0:37:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夜空中最亮的星星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are the brightest stars in our night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.72,0:37:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人马座α是除太阳之外离地球最近的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Centaurus holds Alpha Centauri...the star nearest to the Earth after our own Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.36,0:37:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细观察会发现人马座α\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And a closer look reveals that Alpha Centauri...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.27,0:37:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上是个三合星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is actually a triple star system.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.74,0:37:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星与一两个伴星联合出镜演出并不罕见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's not unusual for stars to share the spotlight...with one or two orbiting co-stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.74,0:37:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 那是常态\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln fact, it's the norm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.54,0:37:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在天上看到的星星六成以上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Over 60 percent of the stars you see in the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.75,0:37:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上是双星 三星 四星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are actually double stars, triple stars, quadruple stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.46,0:37:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的太阳是个例外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our Sun is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.84,0:37:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的太阳明显没有伴星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our Sun apparently has no companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.26,0:37:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在太阳独步太空时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}While our Sun makes its lonely voyage through space...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.68,0:37:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半人马座奥米茄星团从来就不缺伴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the stars of Omega Centauri never lack company.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.60,0:37:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是最亮的球状星团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt is the brightest globular star cluster...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.15,0:38:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以不用望远镜肉眼就能看到它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that you can see without a telescope...just with the naked eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.73,0:38:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 那是个包括1000万颗星星的巨大星团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because it is a giant cluster of about10 million stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.49,0:38:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半人马座奥米茄星团是银河系里最大的星团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Omega Centauri is the largest star cluster in our galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.70,0:38:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些抱团在一起的星星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These tightly bound stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.58,0:38:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着各种复杂的轨道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all have different, complicated orbits...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.75,0:38:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 它们依然设法一起活动形成一个群体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but they still manage to move together as a single group.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.88,0:38:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星团的出身无人知晓\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Where the cluster comes from is anyone's guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.09,0:38:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个与众不同的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's an unusual object...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.63,0:38:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多天文学家猜测\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and a lot of astronomers suspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.43,0:38:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有可能是路过却被银河系吞噬了的星系的中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that this might be the center of a galaxy...which got eaten or consumed by the Milky Way...when it fell in.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.60,0:38:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情肯定发生频繁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That certainly happens fairly of often...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.85,0:38:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大鱼吃小鱼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that big galaxies are cannibals...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.44,0:38:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大星系吃小星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they eat little galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.77,0:38:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半人马座奥米茄星团可能就是那个过程的残留物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And Omega Centauri may be a remnant of this process.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.07,0:38:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人马座α发出的光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The light from Alpha Centauri...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.45,0:38:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要4.2年达到地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}takes about 4.2 years to reach us...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.12,0:38:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们看到的半人马座奥米茄星团的光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but when we look at Omega Centauri...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.04,0:39:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是1.6万年前发出的光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we're seeing light that's traveled 16,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.25,0:39:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由此可见半人马座实际有多大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's some indication of how large Centaurus really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.05,0:39:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也表明星座的存在只是我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt also shows that a constellation exists...only in our mind's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.55,0:39:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每颗星都像一件艺术品\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And each star, like every piece of art...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.72,0:39:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有待探索\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}begs to be explored.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.94,0:39:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座组织起夜空 让它易于了解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The constellations organize the night sky and make it almost comprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.32,0:39:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们凝视闪烁的星光时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As we gaze at the twinkling lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.82,0:39:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很容易忘却\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's easy to forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.91,0:39:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一颗都是数十亿颗炙热的太阳中的一员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that each is one of billions of blazing suns...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.95,0:39:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在融合元素并且可能在创造新的世界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}fusing elements and possibly creating new worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.29,0:39:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的距离使得我们感觉不到星星的力量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our distance gives us no sense of the stars' power.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.88,0:39:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让我们感觉不到我们眼中的太空的深邃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt also gives us no sense...of the endless depth of space we're peering into.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.18,0:39:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平面的星座是一种错觉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The flat planes of the constellations...are an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.93,0:40:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你从太阳动身启程\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As you start getting away from the Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.10,0:40:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过几光年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by several light-years...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.35,0:40:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近的星星相对更为遥远的背景星开始移动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the nearby stars begin shif ting...relative to the more distant background stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.99,0:40:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样星座就开始变形\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the constellations start distorting.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.70,0:40:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你出去10 20 30光年后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By the time you are out at10, 20, 30 light-years...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.45,0:40:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你或许就辨认不出有些星座了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you probably wouldn't recognize few of the constellations.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.83,0:40:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果你居住在织女星的行星上 也就是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So if you lived on a planet going around Vega, let's say...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.21,0:40:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离这里25光年远\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that's 25 light-years away from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.09,0:40:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会看到空中有别样的星座组合\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you'd have a different set of constellations in your sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.39,0:40:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年的望星已经让星座的壮丽扫视\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Millennia of stargazing have made the grand sweep...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.01,0:40:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得平淡乏味\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the constellations predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.39,0:40:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们围绕着太阳转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our rotation around the Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.48,0:40:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着我们周而复始 年复一年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}carries us through their annual cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.61,0:40:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座里的群星不停地移动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The stars in the constellations are in constant motion...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.48,0:40:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不但随着星系打转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}not just as the galaxy spins...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.74,0:40:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时 还由于各自的引力牵引 相互拽拉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but also as each star"s gravity tugs and pulls on its neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.24,0:41:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运动最快的星星有每秒150英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The fastest motion of the stars is150 miles per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.66,0:41:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何人造物体能赶上它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We don't have any manmade object that can go that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.79,0:41:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于这些星星相互之间的无规则运动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The random motions of these stars...with respect to each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.26,0:41:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更像是每秒10到20英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are more like 10 or 20 miles a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.13,0:41:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比得上我们最快的飞船的速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that is comparable to the speed...of our fastest spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.60,0:41:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然远远快过高速子弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's, of course, way, way faster...than a high-speed bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.02,0:41:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星一直在运动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The stars are always moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.15,0:41:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们与我们之间的距离掩饰了其巨大的速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and their distance from us masks their enormous speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.53,0:41:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是从疾驶的汽车车窗看出去一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's like looking out the window of a speeding automobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.36,0:41:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路旁的栅栏柱和树木呼啸而过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The fence posts and trees closest to the highway...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.78,0:41:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而远景却在缓缓过去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}whiz by,while the distant landscape creeps slowly past.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.37,0:41:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一生 事实上 在近一千个人生时段里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Over our lifetime...in fact, close to a thousand lifetimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.92,0:41:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多数星星看上去根本就没动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}most stars don't appear to move at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.59,0:41:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不禁让我想到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt just intrigues me to think...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.80,0:42:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能找到一个近亲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that if l could find one of our recent relatives...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.72,0:42:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如克罗马努人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Cro-Magnon man, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.14,0:42:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他或许会纠正我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he would probably correct me...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.43,0:42:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 他会对天空更为熟悉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because he would be more familiar with the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.06,0:42:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对星座会比现代人了解得更多一些\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and he would know the constellations...a little bit better than the people do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.15,0:42:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而慢慢的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But little by little...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.69,0:42:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的星图正度过有效期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}our star maps are reaching their expiration dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.53,0:42:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一万年里星星将明显不一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln 10,000 years, the stars...would be noticeably different.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.87,0:42:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座将明显不同于我们现在所见到模样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The constellations would be noticeably different...than what we see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.33,0:42:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,50万年里它们将面目全非\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln 500,000 years, they will be unrecognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.79,0:42:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 你真能看到百万年里的慢镜头照片的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if you truly could see a time-lapse photo...over a period of a million years...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.63,0:42:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 你会看到群星在天上赛跑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you would, in fact, see stars racing around the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.84,0:42:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座是快照\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The constellations are a snapshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.26,0:42:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夜空的平面肖像\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a flattened portrait of the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.43,0:42:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和肖像一样 是生动的写照\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And like a portrait, it's a good likeness...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.85,0:42:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是整个故事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but not the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.98,0:42:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们可以飞进太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf we could fly into space...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.44,0:42:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从另一个角度去看它们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and see them from another angle...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.19,0:42:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些古老熟悉的排列将会难以识别\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}these old, familiar starformations...would be unidentifiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.90,0:42:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 此时此地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But right here, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.65,0:43:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,88个星座提供着可靠的路标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the 88 constellations provide reassuring guideposts...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.70,0:43:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时让我们缅怀过去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}while reminding us of our past.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.37,0:43:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座确实没有履行起人们当初设计它们时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The constellations really don't fulfill the functions...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.12,0:43:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所赋予它们的职能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that they fulfilled originally...for the people that devised them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.54,0:43:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他们来说 在他们感兴趣的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For them, there was a direct cause-and-effect connection...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.71,0:43:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与他们的寿命之间存在着一个直接的因果关系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}between something that was of interest to them...and their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.88,0:43:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们观察天狼星是因为它是季节的指示\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They watched Sirius because it was a seasonal indicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.39,0:43:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再也不会那样利用天空了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We don't use the sky that way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.89,0:43:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 故事是有弹性的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the stories are resilient...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.89,0:43:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图像也是有弹性的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the images are resilient.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.94,0:43:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们守住了那些星座\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We hold onto those constellations...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.73,0:43:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦率地说 我很高兴 我们这么做了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and frankly, l'm delighted we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.23,0:43:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是诉说过去的故事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lnstead of telling stories of the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.70,0:43:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现代天文学迫使我们观察星座\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}modern astronomy compels us to look at constellations...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.49,0:43:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为可利用的分类\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as a grouping of possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.12,0:43:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分星座\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most of the constellations...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.25,0:43:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里头都会有三五个行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have three to five planets inside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.04,0:43:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过几年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And in a few more years...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.92,0:43:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将找到或许数百个类地行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we're gonna identify...perhaps hundreds of Earth-like planets...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.75,0:43:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围绕着别的恒星运转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}orbiting other stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.67,0:44:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们每晚都心怀虔诚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So we will have this epiphany every night...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.30,0:44:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意识到在我们注视星座时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}realizing that when we look at the constellations...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.76,0:44:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定有人在看我们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}somebody may be looking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.93,0:44:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在茫茫太空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln a space so vast...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.64,0:44:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能看到宇宙的很小一部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we can only see...a small fraction of our universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.60,0:44:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看着星空 思量着它的全部含义\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we look to the stars, wondering what it all means...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.44,0:44:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,编制图案 编造故事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}making patterns, inventing stories...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.28,0:44:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力解答着星座里头的秘密\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}attempting to solve the mysteries...that our constellations hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.20,0:44:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢观赏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thanks For Viewing
